Interface RMeshParserEventsType<E extends Throwable>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of exceptions raised.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RMeshParserEventsVBO

    public interface RMeshParserEventsType<E extends Throwable>
    An interface that accepts events from a mesh parser.
